GENERIC: make-pred-quot ( predicate-word class -- quot )

! { real fixnum array }
! [ dup real? [ nip ] [ dup fixnum? [ nip ] [ array? ] if* ] if* ]
M: union-class make-pred-quot nip
    "members" word-prop <reversed> unclip "predicate" word-prop
